OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry and warm
OL,6,Fthroughout the day with plenty of
OL,7,Flengthy sunny spells. Sunshine turning
OL,8,Fhazier in the afternoon with some high-
OL,9,Flevel cloud spreading south.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first with some hazy
OL,12,Fevening sunshine. It will gradually
OL,13,Fcloud over from the north through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight with the odd
OL,15,Fspot of light rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,18,Fpatchy light rain possible. Staying
OL,19,Flargely cloudy through the day but
OL,20,Fperhaps brightening up somewhat as
OL,21,Fcloud starts to break at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
