OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstarts with some patchy light rain in
OL,7,Fthe north. Warm sunny intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping in the south through the
OL,9,Fafternoons, staying cloudier and
OL,10,Fcooler in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
